    "In 2023, Anna's Archive foot_7 became the world's largest open-source and opendata library.",
    "The creator scraped books from libraries such as Libgen, Sci-Hub, and made them publicly available.",
    "As of February 2024, its size has reached 641.2TB and it is continuously growing.",
    "It is worth mentioning that the fields covered by books are extremely diverse.",
    "Thus, fine-grained categorization of books by domain is feasible."
